  <p class="en" style="font-size:.85rem;color:#71717a">Sources: The official Ethereum EIP-7928 specification (eips.ethereum.org) and Ethereum Magicians forum discussion, the Glamsterdam roadmap (ethereum.org, including EIP-7732's proposer-builder separation), Glamsterdam and EIP-7928 explainers from Everstake and BingX, and, for historical reference, EIP-2930 (2021 Berlin upgrade) and documentation on Solana's Sealevel parallel runtime. Activation timing, the gas limit and performance figures remain an unconfirmed, forward-looking plan and set of targets; this is not investment advice.</p>
